<h1 id="toc0"><span>Congratulations to our winners, Team Clever Gentlemen, our runners up, Team I Don't Want to Die, and our bronze medalists Fuhgeddaboutit!</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc1"><span>And thank you to all who participated; we very literally wouldn't have had a contest without you guys.</span></h2>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Full&nbsp;Results</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Go&nbsp;away.</a></div>
